{"tid":1083333,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 身上有好多不知明紅點","createTime":"2019-03-29T14:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T06:21:55.000Z","uid":82608,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7b31f1b95ea57e0f5f6895cd3090adc8f1024b56","tid":1083333,"uid":82608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話說上星期小弟身上起左兩三粒兩隻手指公咁大嘅紅斑，唔癢唔痛，但紅斑中間會慢慢甩左一層薄薄嘅皮<br />\n<br />\n但最近呢兩日身上開始起左好多粒細細粒腫起嘅紅點，成個上半身同背脊都係，愈起愈密，但下半身同手腳一啲事都冇<br />\n<br />\n有懷疑係咪有床蝨咬，但我同女朋友一齊訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢乜事都冇，同埋上網睇過床蝨咬嘅相，同我嘅狀況一啲都唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇ching試過，知道發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf37c314fd327b20328d85eb4a5f1ec69f6614e","tid":1083333,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78cf5531b31c1395811cdac1349be95088bfbeab","tid":1083333,"uid":82608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf37c314fd327b20328d85eb4a5f1ec69f6614e","tid":1083333,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62610325931b413dbe6b83b3568b43829aba7ce5","tid":1083333,"uid":27946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a7e201969c7fb48ff3fde1c04db811574b4c1","tid":1083333,"uid":27416,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"條女係出面惹到傳俾你"},{"pid":"c18ef165